        <title>EGR Drive Module</title>
        <para>Inspect the EGR drive module and replace if necessary. Check for the following:</para>
        <randlist type="bullet">
            <item>
                <para>Bent connector pins.</para>
            </item>
            <item>
                <para>Corrosion to the pins or module.</para>
            </item>
            <item>
                <para>Heat damage to the module.</para>
            </item>
        </randlist>
